Comment: 0,0:00:41.12,0:00:41.14,Ch,,0,0,0,,## 主歌-1
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.12,0:00:44.72,Ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}我最近都活在自己的腦袋裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.12,0:00:44.72,En,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}I've been living in my mind for some time
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.82,0:00:50.29,Ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}以為你已經明白；跟我的罪行看開
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.82,0:00:50.29,En,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}thought that you had understood; made peace with my crimes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.84,0:00:55.29,Ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}現在我坐在這邊，桌子空空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.84,0:00:55.29,En,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Now I'm sitting here with nothing on the table
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.74,0:00:59.67,Ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}又只有我的心跟靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.74,0:00:59.67,En,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}but my heart and my soul, again
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.49,0:01:02.84,Ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}每位小馬都
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.49,0:01:02.84,En,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Everypony talks
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.84,0:01:05.29,Ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}談吐著渺小的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.84,0:01:05.29,En,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}about their little dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.39,0:01:09.47,Ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}但我還在追隨我丟下的心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.39,0:01:09.47,En,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}but I'm still following the heart I left behind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.02,0:01:12.34,Ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}現在我就是給怪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.02,0:01:12.34,En,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Now I'm the one to blame
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.37,0:01:14.79,Ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}全部倒在我頭頂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.37,0:01:14.79,En,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Just take it out on me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.79,0:01:17.17,Ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}一直來都是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.79,0:01:17.17,En,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}It's always been this way
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.17,0:01:19.69,Ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}你看來還不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.17,0:01:19.69,En,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}something you've never seen
Comment: 0,0:01:19.74,0:01:19.75,Ch,,0,0,0,,## 副歌
