Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.74,0:02:04.17,En,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Never been your coat
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.17,0:02:05.24,Ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}你的，好嗎
