Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.65,0:02:13.14,Ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}但魔法讓我開心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.64,0:02:13.14,En,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}but it keeps me feeling good
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.24,0:02:15.59,Ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}你沒什麼選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.24,0:02:15.59,En,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Pick your poison now
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.59,0:02:17.40,Ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}體驗我的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.59,0:02:17.39,En,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}to stand where I've stood
